{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0001","text":"愛也要講資格 我有什麼資格","structure":{"line_index":1,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情資格","自我懷疑"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["資格","愛"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,5,4,9,3,4,5,5,2,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["oi3","jaa5","jiu3","gong2","zi1","gaak3","ngo5","jau5","sam6","mo1","zi1","gaak3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"資格","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"什麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"資格","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"以問句表達對自身條件的質疑，語氣帶有失落感。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":null,"next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0002","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0002","text":"你若靠向她 總可算合理抉擇","structure":{"line_index":2,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["感情轉移","合理化"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["靠向","合理","抉擇"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,4,4,3,9,9,4,2,5,4,2],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["nei5","joek6","kaau3","hoeng3","taa1","zung2","ho2","syun3","hap6","lei5","kyut3","zaak6"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"靠","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"向","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"她","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"總可算","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"合理","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"抉擇","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"假設對方與第三者的關係，並認為這是合理的選擇，語氣趨於平淡。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0001","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0003","paragraph_id":"para_01"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0003","text":"我每晚都咳嗽 自你有最新好友","structure":{"line_index":3,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["身體不適","被冷落"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["咳嗽","好友"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,3,3,4,2,5,5,4,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","mui5","maan5","dou1","kat1","sau3","zi6","nei5","jau5","zeoi3","san1","hou2","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"每晚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"咳嗽","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"自","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"最新","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"好友","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描述自身身體狀況，並暗示對方已有新對象，形成對比。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0002","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0004","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0004","text":"但你偏痛切慰問 病菌怎麼會纏身","structure":{"line_index":4,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["關懷","諷刺"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["慰問","病菌","纏身"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,3,4,4,4,2,2,9,9,3,0,3],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","nei5","pin1","tung3","cai3","wai3","man6","beng6","kwan2","zam2","mo1","cin4","san1"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"偏","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"痛切","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"慰問","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"病菌","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"怎麼","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"纏身","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"對比自己生病卻被對方慰問，語氣帶有諷刺，暗示對方對自己的病況的關心是出於禮貌或諷刺。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0003","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0005","paragraph_id":"para_02"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0005","text":"我若再依戀你 定會加重我這病情","structure":{"line_index":5,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["病情惡化","依戀的代價"],"sentiment":"VERY_NEGATIVE","keywords":["依戀","加重","病情"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,2,4,3,9,5,2,3,5,5,2,0],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ngo5","joek6","zoi3","ji1","lyun2","nei5","ding6","gaa1","ngo5","ze5","beng6","cing4"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"若","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"再","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"依戀","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"定","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"會","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"加重","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"這","pos":"DET"},{"text":"病情","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"將對方的離去比喻為病情加重，表達依戀的痛苦與代價。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0004","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0006","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0006","text":"只盼在這天起忘掉你 用放棄來治療絕症","structure":{"line_index":6,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["放棄治療","自我療癒"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["忘掉","放棄","治療","絕症"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[9,4,2,5,3,9,0,2,5,2,4,4,0,2,0,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["zi2","paan3","zoi6","ze5","tin1","hei2","mong4","diu6","nei5","jung6","fong3","hei3","loi4","zi6","liu4","zyut6","zing3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"只","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"盼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"在","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"這天","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"起","pos":"PART"},{"text":"忘掉","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"用","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"放棄","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"來","pos":"PART"},{"text":"治療","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"絕症","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"表達決心忘記對方，並將放棄這段關係視為治療絕症的方法，語氣轉為積極。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0005","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0007","paragraph_id":"para_03"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0007","text":"明白到分手都要好好保重 不要有病痛","structure":{"line_index":7,"char_count":16},"semantics":{"themes":["分手後的自我照顧","康復"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["保重","病痛"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,3,9,3,4,9,9,9,3,4,5,2,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ming4","baak6","dou3","fan1","sau2","dou1","jiu3","hou2","hou2","bou2","bat1","jiu3","jau5","beng6","tung3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"明白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"PART"},{"text":"分手","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"都","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"好好","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"保重","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不要","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"有","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"病痛","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"領悟到分手後也要好好照顧自己，避免身心受創，語氣趨於平靜與堅定。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0006","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0008","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0008","text":"蓋著那厚外套 替代天冷被你擁抱","structure":{"line_index":8,"char_count":14},"semantics":{"themes":["自我安慰","替代"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["外套","替代","擁抱"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,2,5,5,2,4,4,2,3,5,2,5,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["goi3","zoek6","naa5","hau5","ngoi6","tou3","tai3","doi6","tin1","laang5","bei6","nei5","jung2","pou5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"蓋著","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"那厚","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"外套","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"替代","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"天冷","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"被","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"擁抱","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"用具體的行動（穿外套）來比喻替代對方的情感慰藉，語氣平淡。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0007","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0009","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0009","text":"明白到傷心總有一天康復 煙與酒都不碰","structure":{"line_index":9,"char_count":17},"semantics":{"themes":["傷痛復原","戒除不良習慣"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["傷心","康復","煙酒"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,2,4,3,3,9,5,3,3,3,2,3,5,9,3,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ming4","baak6","dou3","soeng1","sam1","zung2","jau5","jat1","tin1","hong1","fuk6","jin1","jyu5","zau2","dou1","bat1","pung3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"明白","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"到","pos":"PART"},{"text":"傷心","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"總有一天","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"康復","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"煙","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"與","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"酒都","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"碰","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"表達傷心終會過去，並承諾戒除不良習慣，展現積極復原的態度。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0008","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0010","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0010","text":"讓你可看到 受了傷也咬著牙來爲創口 貼下膠布","structure":{"line_index":10,"char_count":20},"semantics":{"themes":["堅強面對","自我療傷"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["咬牙","創口","膠布"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,9,4,4,2,5,3,5,5,2,0,0,3,9,4,2,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joeng6","nei5","ho2","hon3","dou3","sau6","liu5","soeng1","jaa5","ngaau5","zoek6","ngaa4","loi4","cong1","hau2","tip3","haa6","gaau1","bou3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"讓","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"可","pos":"AUX"},{"text":"看到","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"受了傷","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"也","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"咬","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"著牙來","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"爲","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"創口","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"貼","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"下","pos":"PART"},{"text":"膠布","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"描寫即使受傷也咬緊牙關，用創可貼來處理傷口，比喻堅強面對痛苦並自我療癒。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0009","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0011","paragraph_id":"para_04"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0011","text":"這晚我失聲了 道別話講不了","structure":{"line_index":11,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["身體不適","無法言語"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["失聲","道別","講不了"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,5,5,3,3,5,2,2,2,9,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["ze5","maan5","ngo5","sat1","sing1","liu5","dou6","bit6","waa6","gong2","bat1","liu5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"這晚","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"失聲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"了","pos":"PART"},{"text":"道別","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"話","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"講","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不了","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"描述因身體不適而失聲，無法說出告別的話，語氣顯得無奈。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0010","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0012","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0012","text":"腳部卻太酸 想走近又走不了","structure":{"line_index":12,"char_count":12},"semantics":{"themes":["身體不適","行動受阻"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["腳部","酸","走不了"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[4,2,4,4,3,9,9,2,2,9,3,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["goek3","bou6","koek3","taai3","syun1","soeng2","zau2","gan6","jau6","zau2","bat1","liu5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"腳部","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"卻","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"太酸","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"想","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"走近","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"又","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"走","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不了","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"描寫腳部痠痛導致行動不便，想靠近卻無法靠近，語氣顯得無力。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0011","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0013","paragraph_id":"para_05"}}
{"id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0013","text":"兩頰變得消瘦 自你搭上新好友","structure":{"line_index":13,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["身體消瘦","被取代"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["消瘦","新好友"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[5,4,4,3,3,4,2,5,4,3,9,5],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["loeng5","gaap3","bin3","dak1","siu1","sau3","zi6","nei5","daap3","san1","hou2","jau5"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"兩頰","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"變得","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"消瘦","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"自","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"搭","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"上","pos":"PART"},{"text":"新","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"好友","pos":"NOUN"}],"syntax_notes":"再次描述身體的消瘦，並提及對方有了新對象，語氣顯得憔悴與無奈。"},"source":{"title":"自己保重","artists":["麥浚龍"],"lyricists":["李峻一"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_5796","prev_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0012","next_line_id":"lyr_6bqm5rWa6b6Z_NTc5Ng_0014","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
